<h2>Dorukyo Clan</h2>

<p>The Dorukyo Clan was initially made to be a one-off clan from Kirigakure who would be considered the most versatile Generalist shinobi, but they have turned into something much more and will be a rather major aspect of IoG as a whole.<br><br>
<b>A Henkan or Dressphere, is an object which has, sealed within in it, information that an individual may access in order to essentially transform into the individual stored within.<br><br>
<b>The Dorukyo use something called Transformation Release to unlock the hidden potential of these items and absorb them, granting them the ability which comes with it. They can also use this for casual affairs, such as changing from a ceremonial garb to a simple attire.<br><br>
<b>This grants them the ability to use it, but not the knowledge on how to use it. For example, if one were to unlock a sphere which obtained the abilities of a samurai, they would be transformed in the attire of a samurai and be given one of their swords, but lack the knowledge and ability to properly utilize the armor and blade.<br><br>
<b>Essentially, they use these spheres to change clothes and profession BUT without the proper training, they'd be at a loss.<br><br>
<b>There are many strengths and weaknesses to this Clan but I won't cover most of them here:<br><br>
<b>Weaknesses: If the spheres are damaged, broken or shattered the members are unable to restore or utilize it any longer; The members of the clan are very vulnerable during their transformations. (1 rp round);Each transformation gives them an alternate personality, and the members are often prone to transitioning between these personalities.<br><br>
<b>Strengths: The members of this clan are very well versed and are known throughout the ninja world for being master generalists due to their wide variety of choices; The spheres they carry around are small and portable, giving them the oppurtunity to use them with ease and transition between transformations; The sphere gives the user whatever clothing, armor, weaponry and abilities that the transformation state had previously.<br><br>
